body: - Fix bug in max-min landmark selector
Added the cyclo-octane dataset example to the Javaplex tutorial.

- Added another example with real data to the Javaplex tutorial, namely the 3-circle model for optical images from "On the Local Behavior of Spaces of Natural Images" by Carlsson, Ishkhanov, de Silva, and Zomorodian.

- fixed non-integer filtration time bug
- various minor changes since last Google Code release are incorporated
